际应用仍有很长一段路要走。 资料来源突破性研究：利用地球自转生成电能"},"attached_info":"CkIIwa3z6M6AlsMxEAMaCTExNDE1ODE5NiD3goi/BjAAOI0BQAlyCzE1Njk0OTIyMTcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"141 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3fc48b349ae0d55221014b0418e376d9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1742998825.268826","card_id":"Q_15328206087","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":15328206087,"title":"比亚迪海狮 05 EV 于 3 月 25 日上市，11.78-13.78 万，该车有哪些亮点？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15328206087","type":"question","created":1742363795,"answer_count":84,"follower_count":172,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[570,1686,13381,60628,239763],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"近日，比亚迪海狮 05 EV 官方图片惊艳亮相，这款纯电动紧凑型 SUV，注定将成为市场的新宠。 它不仅全系标配了先进的天神之眼-C 高阶智能驾驶系统，还搭载了 DiLink 100 智能座舱，为驾驶者带来前所未有的科技体验。 这款新车将于 3 月 25 日正式上市，让众多车迷翘首以待。比亚迪海狮05 EV官图 将于3月25日上市"},"attached_info":"CkIIwa3z6M6AlsMxEAMaCTExNDA1ODQ5MSCTuem+BjAAOKwBQApyCzE1MzI4MjA2MDg3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"137 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0b4837e46e0e22e45c28823f9be736c3_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1742998825.270604","card_id":"Q_662232778","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662232778,"title":"金价暴涨背后的原因是什么呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662232778","type":"question","created":1721598671,"answer_count